{{en-noun}}

# {{label|en|grammar}} An [[exclamation]] or [[filled pause]]; a word or [[phrase]] with no particular grammatical relation to a sentence, often an expression of [[emotion]].
#* {{quote-book|year=1988|author=Andrew Radford|title=Transformational grammar: a first course|location=Cambridge, UK|publisher=Cambridge University Press|page=533|chapter=10}}
